channel.title: Dying for no reason!
channel.description: I have this problem with my delta based server, it isn't exaclty delta but is based from it. Ok well from time to time your character will just drop dead and it will say you defeated yourself. For example "You have defeated Owner Cheese<---- my name". It might be the death timers but im not sure. It pretty much happens all the time when someone first starts off as well. Is it possible I can fix this? If so please dont say things like "D3LT@ 5UK5 Y0U N00B!!1!!PIE". I get a lot of things like that here and its very dissapointing and will need to no help, I just want a soloution or how to fix the problem. I can code a bit so if I have to change things thats ok with me.
